# Eval fixtures are committed: assertions cite exact file:line and must be reproducible
# from a fresh clone. The scanner excludes **/evals/files/** in all three tiers, so the
# intentional anti-patterns inside them cannot fail the repo's own smell-scan CI gate.

# Eval run results (benchmarks, grading, timing)
*-workspace/
.serena/

# test-parity.sh transient backups (stray after an interrupted run)
*.parity-backup
